<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; }
        .header { background-color: #1B3E5D; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .status-box { background-color: #f0f7ff; border-left: 4px solid #1B3E5D; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #1B3E5D; color: white !important; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Obana Logistics</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{customer_name}},</p>
            <p>There is an update on your shipment <strong>{{shipment_reference}}</strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="status-box">
                <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>New Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
            </div>

            {{#if tracking_number}}
            <p><strong>Tracking Number:</strong> {{tracking_number}}</p>
            {{/if}}

            <p>You can track your package in real-time by clicking the button below:</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                {{#if tracking_url}}
                <a href="{{tracking_url}}" class="btn">Track on Carrier Site</a>
                {{else}}
                <a href="{{dashboard_url}}" class="btn">View in Dashboard</a>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Obana Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{year}} Obana Logistics. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>